### Example 03: Route Groups
### Server: http://localhost:3000

### Root
GET http://localhost:3000/

### API v1 - Simple list
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/users

### API v1 - Single user
GET http://localhost:3000/v1/users/1

### API v2 - Enhanced list with metadata
GET http://localhost:3000/v2/users

### API v2 - Single user with metadata
GET http://localhost:3000/v2/users/1

### Admin - Root
GET http://localhost:3000/admin

### Admin - Stats
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/stats

### Admin - Config
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/config

### Admin - List users
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/users

### Admin - Create user
POST http://localhost:3000/admin/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Charlie",
  "email": "charlie@example.com"
}

### Admin - Delete user
DELETE http://localhost:3000/admin/users/1
